lauderdale and west palm beach finally agreed to buy the property 
and city attorney herb thiele announced completion of the sale 
tuesday 
the stores lease expires at midnight july 31 thiele said he 
would not waste any time in shutting down the business 
it is my intention to put chains and a padlock on the doors at 
1201 am august first thiele said 
