against repression 
people say im impulsive that i want to change things too 
quickly but i dont want to wait 100 years i dont want to know my 
daughter will have the same problems i did 
enrolled in the literature department of the university of 
palermo she studies at home and says when she marries her 
boyfriend shell move to gela his town 25 miles from licata 
