to the parks neighborhing sheep meadow a 13acre area decreed a 
quiet zone by mayor edward koch in 1985 and residents of a 
fashionable neighborhood called central park west 
the city policy was challenged by rock against racism which 
sponsors an annual bandshell program of speakers and musical groups 
the case is ward vs rock against racism 88226 
